abstract: Chris Hughes helped create the social network. Now he’s working with academics and government regulators on arguments for dismantling the company.

abstract: Most people hurt themselves when they try to outsmart the markets, the latest data shows. Humility is a better strategy.
snippet: Most people hurt themselves when they try to outsmart the markets, the latest data shows. Humility is a better strategy.
lead_paragraph: Forget about getting everything right. Most people are so consistently wrong that merely avoiding major errors is enough to set you apart from the pack.

abstract: The event, originally planned for upstate New York, was all but dead after the last permit denial. It will be held Aug. 16-18 in Columbia, Md.
snippet: The event, originally planned for upstate New York, was all but dead after the last permit denial. It will be held Aug. 16-18 in Columbia, Md.
lead_paragraph: The producers of Woodstock 50, the troubled anniversary festival, have secured a last-minute deal to put on their show — or at least a version of it — in Maryland, after months of legal and permit battles in upstate New York that had left the event in grave doubt.

abstract: If the president encourages supporters to see the news in simple, cinematic terms, Sebastian Gorka provides the voice-over.
snippet: If the president encourages supporters to see the news in simple, cinematic terms, Sebastian Gorka provides the voice-over.
lead_paragraph: We “shall not live by bread alone,” Jesus said. No, we want more; we want, like Homer Simpson, to experience “the terrifying lows” and “the dizzying highs.” We want blood and guts and meaningful struggle. In civilian life, we seek out surrogate versions of such thrills at the movies. But we’re also, increasingly, finding them in the melodrama of politics — and few are so adept at giving the daily news a cinematic sheen as Sebastian Gorka, a former Trump official whose online commentary makes it sound as though the world were teetering on a razor’s edge at every hour of every day.

abstract: His primary subjects were his family and friends, the many glories of London, and old master paintings in the National Gallery.
snippet: His primary subjects were his family and friends, the many glories of London, and old master paintings in the National Gallery.
lead_paragraph: Leon Kossoff, whose expressionistic portraits and images of urban life made him one of the most important painters of postwar Britain, died on July 4 in London. He was 92.

headline_print_headline: Leon Kossoff, Who Painted Portraits of Urban Life in London, Is Dead at 92

abstract: For the first time, the Trump administration is imposing economic penalties on a Chinese company for importing Iranian oil, a decision certain to add to tensions between Washington and Beijing.
snippet: For the first time, the Trump administration is imposing economic penalties on a Chinese company for importing Iranian oil, a decision certain to add to tensions between Washington and Beijing.
lead_paragraph: The Trump administration is imposing economic sanctions on a Chinese state-owned oil trading company and its top executive for buying Iranian oil in violation of an American ban, Secretary of State Mike Pompeo said Monday.
